    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >首先</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《超级昭和电动画剧☆太空拌饭海苔碎》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >读到这里就别想再逃了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/7421520dc4c536c1c8a75aa982a86439.poster.avif?t=1770695058\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/7421520dc4c536c1c8a75aa982a86439.webm?t=1770695058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/7421520dc4c536c1c8a75aa982a86439.mp4?t=1770695058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情梗概</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身着哥特裙、头戴𫚕鱼、痴迷御宅文化的“小纱”是正在复读的二十岁女生。小莎被意外卷入神秘的时空扭曲，穿越至超级昭和，在当地邂逅了疯狂的女高中生们！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地狱、宇宙、孩童的体内，她们时而被卷入麻烦，时而制造麻烦，毫无畏惧地大肆破坏！她们是百年一遇的麻烦制造者！而触及这个世界谜团的小莎，命运将何去何从……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作好心理准备，豁出去吧！你已无法逃离超级昭和！！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/6277b301d6f4785a19601c35dc5ffefe.avif?t=1770695058\" width=384 height=216 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《超级昭和电动画剧☆太空拌饭海苔碎》是什么？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是由「4t tomatine（よんとんトマチン）」制作的超级昭和搞笑视觉小说。在赛璐璐风格的插画与动画效果中，展开充满动画、游戏、电影、音乐、艺人等恶搞元素的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与主人公小纱一同在充满日本风情的神秘世界，开始一场大冒险吧！途中小莎将被卷入各种麻烦，和各种五花八门的角色建立奇妙的交流！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >预计游戏时长相当于12集电视动画+OVA篇幅。收录全7个章节，所有剧情都以眼花缭乱的动效和惊人节奏推进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含混响版在内的30余首BGM、片头曲、片尾曲均由OCIRCO RECORDS（おしるこレコーズ）的牵头者Taroomi（たろおみ）负责制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更包含占卜、词语接龙等小游戏元素！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请一定要来亲身体验一下哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭载令人怀念的“超级昭和滤镜”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/bde80474d9797edf5b5e3d192f050323.poster.avif?t=1770695058\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/bde80474d9797edf5b5e3d192f050323.webm?t=1770695058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/bde80474d9797edf5b5e3d192f050323.mp4?t=1770695058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开启滤镜瞬间，画面神奇地变身为怀旧的大屁股电视风格！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情沉浸于浓郁的超级昭和情怀中吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打开滤镜效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/9c8da49358b8ff50aff7454d6c76fff1.avif?t=1770695058\" width=382 height=215 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关闭滤镜效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/f4c8da708e6cbc03a30b4cf7e85f3373.avif?t=1770695058\" width=382 height=215 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小莎和快乐的小伙伴们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/5c5d5f5ce027c28e9376f1666faeff14.avif?t=1770695058\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小纱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >二十岁复读生，热衷哥特裙子。通晓各类御宅族与亚文化知识。虽常被卷入麻烦却凭着韧性总能化险为夷。头上的𫚕鱼发箍等饰品均为自制。属于平时不起眼，但关键时刻会发力的那类人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/e43f3737afc08180121c232a2e7f9845.avif?t=1770695058\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竟金镜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >私立海苔学园高二学生。心地非常善良，会对有苦难的人伸出援手，却也常因缺乏常识惹出麻烦。曾在烹饪课制作蛋糕时，出于善意往面糊里加入捡来的小龙虾。视力1.8。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/bc050b539b74f08beec07eeb95f9cafa.avif?t=1770695058\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雷帝院龙子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >私立海苔学园高二学生。与竟金镜同班的高傲千金。身为雷帝院财阀独生女，其父兼任学园理事长。制服内置多种武器原型装置，能从掌心发射光线。手巧且具备顽强生存力，即便不靠家产也能自力更生。反而花钱时容易出事故。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/1c9866ae3af68cc4e9f60c8b425b8903.avif?t=1770695058\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿塔克·安仓纱季</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性别年龄不明的轻浮外星人。无论怎么看都是派来潜伏于地球的间谍。头戴天使光环般的发饰，自以为完美伪装成了地球人。行为虽离奇古怪，但经验知识丰富，有时也会非常冷静。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/5338ce8682c68c3044e5f9582b927cb1.avif?t=1770695058\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >波波天</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阎王约六岁的小女儿。虽是地狱偶像级存在，却因被迫拍摄过激影像而身心俱疲。最爱吃榛石巧克力，食量惊人且拥有地狱出生之人特有的最强消化器官。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/dae6f1dd4b5c4253ee6dd3de08175add.avif?t=1770695058\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盾野芙烈亚</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >私立海苔学园高二学生。深爱着历经沧桑的日本。虽立志征战太空网球甲子园，却因学校不承认网球社团而愤愤不平。自小学起便与竟金镜、雷帝院龙子结下梁子。时常空谈精神，锻炼时有人喝水就会发表。虽然易怒难以接近，实则有着催人泪下的过去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《超级昭和大辞典》助你轻松学习日本文化！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《超级昭和大辞典》收录700余个词条，能让你(自以为)了解超级昭和的世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增大量专为中文版设计的复杂日式文化解析词条！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快把你学到的知识分享给家人、同学和同事吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《超级昭和电动画剧☆太空拌饭海苔碎》的超强亮点！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极具视觉冲击的超级昭和界面！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >满溢御宅文化与亚文化致敬元素！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创BGM超过30首！（还有JAPANESE传统音头曲哦）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超多特效！食欲旺盛！成长迅速！破坏力惊人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更附带催泪小游戏环节！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >促进血液循环！损害视力！恢复电视机夺走的专注力！（相较于本公司其他产品）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量角色齐聚助阵《超级昭和电动画剧☆太空拌饭海苔碎》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直播规范</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摘自私立海苔学园校规</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >─第五条─ 有关游戏直播</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其一</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时禁止食用虫子；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其二</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >禁止上传或直播未经过任何编辑的影像、或没有语音讲解的影像；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其三</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论何时都不可擅自往面条内加醋；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其四</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视频或直播的简介内必须附上《超级昭和电动画剧☆太空拌饭海苔碎》的购买链接；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其五</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >香蕉即使腐烂也不丢弃，必须加工成香蕉蛋糕或果酱等食用；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其六</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在视频或直播过程中，需至少一次引导观众购买《超级昭和电动画剧☆太空拌饭海苔碎》；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其七</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喝酒后要喝同等量的水。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《太空海苔》热烈欢迎游戏视频/直播！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1764700/extras/ac0240761ce8146b195597c80840c46f.avif?t=1770695058\" width=300 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超级昭和等着大家的到来！</p>",
